		<title>E’ morto Sergio Bonelli</title>
		<link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/feedburner/spVB/~3/jdTYRdCblQs/</link>
		<comments>http://www.magrathea.it/2011/09/e-morto-sergio-bonelli/#comments</comments>
