		<title>25 anni di Future Shock: Michele Nigro intervista Antonio Scacco</title>
		<link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/feedburner/spVB/~3/aify3njilzY/</link>
		<comments>http://www.magrathea.it/2011/09/25-anni-di-future-shock-michele-nigro-intervista-antonio-sacco/#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Wed, 21 Sep 2011 10:35:48 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator>magratheastorie</dc:creator>
